### Create Branch
curl -X 'POST' \
  'http://localhost:8282/api/v1/auth/branches' \
  -H 'accept: application/json' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
  "address": "string",
  "branch_code": "string",
  "lat": 0,
  "lng": 0,
  "name": "string",
  "parent_branch_code": "string",
  "radius": 0
}'

